item.title: CVE-2019-10380|2024-08-04T22:17:20.571Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20simple%20travis%20pipeline%20runner%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Simple Travis Pipeline Runner Plugin 1.0 and earlier specifies unsafe values in its custom Script Security whitelist, allowing attackers able to execute Script Security protected scripts to execute arbitrary code.
